{"tid":536723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太子黨後代定居香港搵真銀","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T08:26:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d5f1c7dbbb25e79811d3475a7fcac969e91d59","tid":536723,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180122/20281888?_ga=2.232156831.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F20281888%3F_ga%3D2.232156831.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435&d=2sqDBBqJzP5ZBWXjfw5LSaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4e5c5a49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F20281888%3F_ga%3D2.232156831.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435&h=3077c8b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180122/20281888?_ga=2.232156831.1484461583.1516254068-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n太子黨後代定居香港搵真銀<br />\n<br />\n12,350<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180122/large/a1203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180122%2Flarge%2Fa1203a.gif&h=b2b6ee55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■葉靜子曾與前財爺梁錦松傳緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳曉丹被爆下嫁香港才俊，再次證實「東方之珠」魅力依然。查實，中共太子黨和其後代在港早已密集成群，儘管他們的父輩刻意要「染紅」，並改變香港的社會制度，但私底下他們對港原有制度卻念茲在茲，回歸前這樣，回歸後依然如故。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n京治港確保親友利益<br />\n<br />\n中共元帥葉劍英家族後代不少在港生活定居，如葉的孫女葉靜子曾以香港星際文化集團董事總經理身份出現；中共前政治局常委兼全國政協主席賈慶林的女兒女婿都住港，賈的外孫女、90後的李紫丹更在港島半山坐擁價值逾3億元豪宅；總書記習近平的姐姐齊橋橋（跟母姓）一家早年也定居香港，後才移民澳洲，而習的姪女張燕南曾在港開公司並置業，物業價值6億港幣；現任中共現政治局常委栗戰書的千金栗潛心任職本港金融界高管，與丈夫蔡華波住赤柱豪宅。而這中共已故元老萬里孫女萬寶寶，經常現身香港社交場合。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，香港早已成為中共太子黨們「搵真銀」樂園和移民西方的跳板。有評論指，北京領導人之所以在意對港的有效管治，因為他們的子孫後人、親朋好友不少在港做生意、搵大錢，只有這樣才能確保他們在港的利益「不受影響」！<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n薄熙來涉案受查　丹瓜戀無疾而終<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n#MeToo蔓延內地　大學百教師聯署反性侵"},{"pid":"0e8ac581ae5da0036597dec27257e81a6d59d575","tid":536723,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"一早知<br />\n所以這個地方早不是香港人擁有<br />\n<br />\n什麼本土派 在佢地眼中什麼都不是<br />\n只是比一般市民更賤的存在"},{"pid":"97b93f3c055588e338132fa2b70ee0e10288829f","tid":536723,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e8ac581ae5da0036597dec27257e81a6d59d575","tid":536723,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"一早知<br />\n所以這個地方早不是香港人擁有<br />\n<br />\n什麼本土派 在佢地眼中什麼都不是<br />\n只是比一般市民更賤的存在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:08:45.000Z","msg":"而家香港人面對既全球第2大超級國家<br />\n所以真係無正面的勝算"},{"pid":"234514a72db0ad1237f7e4bbecad60c32c633af9","tid":536723,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"香港=洗黑錢天堂"},{"pid":"21e7252a7edb743cf7e5bf5b43d1a28aa040f8c9","tid":536723,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"萬里個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a56bd4939d6db31a03920328e537ce93dac33b","tid":536723,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e7252a7edb743cf7e5bf5b43d1a28aa040f8c9","tid":536723,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"萬里個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"孫女先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee02e614aad7fc6c954f72cbf2eba9fffabfe9c","tid":536723,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"指定動作 香港住 有美國籍"},{"pid":"72639317f64cdf7e5cd584bfc7c5a57703efe20a","tid":536723,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"今時今日興red blood唔興blue blood"},{"pid":"7959427dc9795b1e07c20d95e49c79a10ee7c972","tid":536723,"uid":88650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"大陸人改名點解可以咁撚求其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩瓜瓜 寶寶"},{"pid":"b8b4c01edd83ba2b2a93f266841b883d4fddcce2","tid":536723,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72639317f64cdf7e5cd584bfc7c5a57703efe20a","tid":536723,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"今時今日興red blood唔興blue blood"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"所以我真係唔明點解港人要怕邊緣化<br />\n根本係要保持優勢去lead住成個中國<br />\n而家香港人呢個名臭哂"}]}